title: Animal Caretakers
descr: Feed, water, groom, bathe, exercise, or otherwise provide care to promote and maintain the well-being of pets and other animals that are not raised for consumption, such as dogs, cats, race horses, ornamental fish or birds, zoo animals, and mice. May clean, disinfect, and repair cages, pens, or fish tanks.
